Implemented functions

Source: R/regression_model.R
supported_functions.Rd

Library of supported functions. The list name and "descr" element should be unique for each element on list.

Usage

supported_functions()

Value

list

Examples

supported_functions()
#> $lm
#> $lm$descr
#> [1] "Linear regression model"
#> 
#> $lm$design
#> [1] "cross-sectional"
#> 
#> $lm$out.type
#> [1] "continuous"
#> 
#> $lm$fun
#> [1] "stats::lm"
#> 
#> $lm$args.list
#> NULL
#> 
#> $lm$formula.str
#> [1] "{outcome.str}~{paste(vars,collapse='+')}"
#> 
#> $lm$table.fun
#> [1] "gtsummary::tbl_regression"
#> 
#> $lm$table.args.list
#> $lm$table.args.list$exponentiate
#> [1] FALSE
#> 
#>
